            <p>This not an issue</p>

<p>Assigning of the parameter <em>bootstrap</em> is done through of the called Zend_Application_Bootstrap_Bootstrap::run().</p>

<p>That happens in Zend_Test_PHPUnit_ControllerTestCase::dispatch() there need that the property Zend_Test_PHPUnit_ControllerTestCase::bootstrap is instance of of <em>Zend_Application</em>.</p>

<p>Simply make a change in setUp().</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function setUp()
{
    $this-&gt;bootstrap = new Zend_Application(
            APPLICATION_ENV,
            APPLICATION_PATH . '/configs/application.ini'
    );
    parent::setUp();
}
</code></pre>

